        "title": "Perimeter Security",
        "content": "Perimeter Security protects the network boundary from external threats. It acts as the first line of defense against unauthorized access and malicious attacks."
      },
      {
        "title": "Network Segmentation",
        "content": "Network Segmentation divides the network into segments to limit access and reduce vulnerabilities. This approach minimizes the potential impact of a breach by isolating sensitive areas."
      },
      {
        "title": "Threat Modeling",
        "content": "Threat Modeling is a proactive approach to identify potential threats and vulnerabilities. Understanding threat actors and their motives helps in designing effective security measures."
      }
    ]
  }
